{"tid":770824,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有圖 岩岩食完大家樂冬瓜盅","createTime":"2018-08-07T11:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T06:02:21.000Z","uid":53209,"like":12,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f3445d313ed758cd8bdb228b7758e50b6a5165","tid":770824,"uid":53209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/07/X0S4xm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F07%2FX0S4xm.jpg&h=92ba8b84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細細個就好鐘意食冬瓜盅<br />\n見大家樂出左就去試下<br />\n<br />\n唔知做乜春大家樂好多大陸仔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見個收銀 係咁講普通話 然後d大陸仔又數券又數銀 買個快餐都搞5分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個餸係 唔知乜春豬軟骨  無期望但居然無失望 幾好食 係少左d<br />\n<br />\n個冬瓜盅 料就唔多 都係肉碎 少量既蝦仁 冬菇 之類 不過食得冬瓜盅都係想食冬瓜 <br />\nd料其實我唔care<br />\nd冬瓜 味道淡左d 唔多入味 但都可以<br />\n湯都係個d野 正常口味<br />\n另外 湯份量極多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我叫左多飯 本身碗飯已經幾多下 再多埋飯 再加個極多份量既冬瓜盅 頂到上心口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n62蚊 依家有d濕9優惠 減10蚊 埋單52蚊<br />\n<br />\n性價比無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e0688b98f30d33311539f4b7c8a24d8093a94e","tid":770824,"uid":198583,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T12:02:29.000Z","msg":"大家樂係咪就執要請網絡打手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac37f5d75da086036c2ee3748aed7c04d4b75a1","tid":770824,"uid":172485,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T12:05:51.000Z","msg":"食大快活啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f18ac1fc80d04de9f28e926d6229804ce3c4910","tid":770824,"uid":50740,"like":1,"